{
  "stem": "1338.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And on the other side, there was a camp, which people were primarily gypsies and some others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They called it gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's why I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But actually, there were other people who were really ready to either be transported somewhere else or prefer-- probably to be eliminated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And just an example of a story that may be relevant, a classmate of mine-- I don't know [INAUDIBLE] classmate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Certainly worked with me in the telephone company.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We became very friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember he had a girlfriend, and they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remembered them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Somehow or other I remember him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ran into him in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a brother and a father in the gypsy camp, and he had the mother in the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was the transfer information.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he would go to the one side and scream through the wires, and they would know to come tomorrow at this time, you know, after whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, he would go to the other side and tell her mother-- his mother what is happening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day he comes to me and he says, you know, my father and my brother were taken away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Taken away is-- is-- is equivalent-- is, well, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is equivalent to saying they were take-- you know, they are gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they're probably gone to-- to the gas chambers, and they are not there anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now he's going to tell his mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he decided, I'm not about to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't want to see her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't want to hear from, you know, her what she's going to do and say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he-- he did something, which I considered at that time-- at that time I considered a classic suicide.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
